title: How Well Do Bobby & Amy Actually Know Each Other? + Walker Hayes Stops By With His Wife Laney For Her Radio Debut
itunes:title: How Well Do Bobby & Amy Actually Know Each Other? + Walker Hayes Stops By With His Wife Laney For Her Radio Debut
description:
Bobby and Amy put their friendship to the test by seeing how much they truly know about each other. Walker Hayes stops by with his wife Laney to talk about his new song "Don't Let Her" that was completely inspired by their relationship. Also, the Girl Group weighs in on husbands checking out other women.
